cdata.name: Bee Token
cdata.desc:
Beenest is a home-sharing platform powered by the Bee Token (BEE) that aims to make the bridge betweenguests and hosts without any commission. The platform is build on top of set Bee Protocols ( Ethereum protocols) that can support other future sharing economy dApps. Moreover, the platform will feature a secure payment system with two authentication P2P entities, a decentralized arbitration system, and a reputation system based on the Ethereum blockchain.

The Bee token (BEE) will be used as the access token to the platform services and also to reward the networkusers.
